The first of a limited collection of castings from THe Elite Redline Guide2 The excessively rare
Brown Charger. Your chance to own the unique signed digital image of this casting directly from
the former owner of this casting, as well as the two authors of THe Elite Redline Guide 2.
 These rare images are part of THe Elite Redline Guide 2 castings. A must-have for any serious collection.
